{"tid":1189053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9號一定要出,但之後香港人要點抗爭?","createTime":"2019-06-06T15:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T19:01:37.000Z","uid":126054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e29177c6e8d2502ce7e4721192ef3b1765050e1","tid":1189053,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"政府建制依家握住香港人行政及立法權<br />\n即係佢想點玩就點玩<br />\n舊有抗爭方式出左咩問題?<br />\n有無新既對抗方法,而且乎合未來既政治、經濟環境?<br />\n希望有見識既巴打解答同討論下"},{"pid":"acca6b9e0ed0efc75235e153447140f2d1b28740","tid":1189053,"uid":7529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"每晚九點半上 twitch 打 comment"},{"pid":"522e9b0762844f1a41436f33554385c918c75a6f","tid":1189053,"uid":78769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:23:02.000Z","msg":"要無賴式游擊(流動)抗爭, 雖然都係冇乜用, 但一定程度上有焦土效果"},{"pid":"9b77ab6e477a17da9bf33fce09f464e68095172f","tid":1189053,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"與其討論著咩衫、唱咩歌、講咩口號<br />\n不如討論下點有新既抗爭<br />\n輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dadcad4c2c1a09f99a992f4ac15a60af6bdfe6e","tid":1189053,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:30:30.000Z","msg":"出左先講，凈系諗唔做唔會有改變，諗唔到未來點做就行左一步得一步先，再隨機應變仲好，始終時勢本身就會隨住當下而改變。就係成日都要最終目標或者結果達成共識，最終就各種分化，反而搞到寸步難行，仲忽略左眼前危機。"},{"pid":"7bc7bd1354f101875a63b0a108cd54e4f8ed55d4","tid":1189053,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yMNhVrZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyMNhVrZ.png&h=0b47e0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1v8pArZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1v8pArZ.png&h=8327c097&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SWtMOM0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn